---
title: Miso Apricot Salmon with Garlic Ginger Rice & Zesty Carrots
description: Fishing for a new twist on salmon? We’ve got just the thing! Crispy skin-on fillets are drizzled with an umami-packed sauce of apricot jam, miso broth, lime juice, and butter. On the side, there’s fluffy, aromatic ginger rice, plus roasted carrots tossed with lime zest. If that doesn’t lure you in, we don’t know what will!
